SQL_STMT_U.val: select MQDT_MQTY_ID, MQDT_DEPT_CODE, MQDT_USRID, MQDT_LINENO, MQDT_DEBC_NO, MQDT_INVO_NO from :1/MQDT where MQDT_MQTY_ID = :2 :3 :4 :5 :6 :7 and (not(exists (select * from :1/DEBH where DEBH_NO = MQDT_DEBH_NO)) or exists (select * from :1/DEBH where DEBH_NO = MQDT_DEBH_NO and not(DEBH_DATDELETED is null))) for fetch only
